            <lg xml:id="TK243">
<l>aruḷcērnta neñciṉārk killai yiruḷcērnta</l>
<l>viṉṉā vulakam pukal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>They will never enter the world of darkness and wretchedness whose minds are the abode of kindness.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
